Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.60,0:00:03.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnArial Black\pos(316,325)\fad(400,0)}Obey the Rules and manners\Nto have a fun Duel!!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.32,0:00:24.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Sometime ago, for the sake of living, we left behind our happiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.33,0:00:31.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We deceived ourselves, clinging to this mere illusion as we danced...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.59,0:00:37.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}With closed eyes, at the end of the horizon,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.93,0:00:43.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I was searching for your smiling face...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.35,0:00:51.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We embrace our dreams and continue on...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.36,0:00:58.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}within the swaying traces of memories...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.20,0:01:05.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Someday, I will once again grasp hold of
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.41,0:01:12.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}these feelings I have locked away in my heart... Now...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.65,0:01:32.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Finally Summoning all three Blue-Eyes,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.36,0:01:34.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Kaiba goes on the attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.57,0:01:38.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I don't have a Monster on the field that can stand up to these attacks...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.86,0:01:43.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Just as I faced certain despair,\N Jounouchi-{\i0}kun{\i1}'s words echoed in my ears.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.87,0:01:48.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's right! There's countless\N possibilities in your hand!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.00,0:01:51.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Fight alongside me,\N Jounouchi-{\i0}kun{\i1}'s Red-Eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.38,0:01:54.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}In order for us to win!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.17,0:02:00.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Defeat the Hatred!\N Black Paladin"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.01,0:02:06.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,B-Big brother...!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.85,0:02:08.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jounouchi-{\i1}kun{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.02,0:02:10.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shizuka...?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.77,0:02:11.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And you guys, too...?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.52,0:02:14.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh...? Where are we?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.07,0:02:15.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why am I here?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.99,0:02:19.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jounouchi, are you really...?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.07,0:02:20.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Honda...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.07,0:02:22.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.03,0:02:23.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Wh-What"...?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.87,0:02:26.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Big brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.08,0:02:28.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Shizuka!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.91,0:02:30.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank Heavens!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.00,0:02:31.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Big brother...!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.58,0:02:33.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shizuka...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.42,0:02:35.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously...! Thank God!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.38,0:02:38.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But this is impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.22,0:02:39.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't believe this!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.43,0:02:42.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just a couple of minutes ago,\N you were on the\N borderline of life and death!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.68,0:02:47.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Last I remember,\N I was Participating in the Domino City\N District Duel Tournament...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.31,0:02:50.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, and then I was suddenly\N watching Yugi's battle...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.31,0:02:51.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Was I dreaming?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.81,0:02:53.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jounouchi! You big jerk!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.77,0:02:55.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell are you\N acting so calm about!?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.98,0:02:57.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Honda-{\i1}san{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.69,0:03:00.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're really awake, aren't you!?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.07,0:03:05.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You damn idiot!\N We all thought you were gonna die!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.28,0:03:07.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't ever die again, asshole!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.70,0:03:08.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Honda...!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.54,0:03:13.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah! I was fighting against Malik!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.96,0:03:14.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What about Mai?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.71,0:03:15.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened to Mai?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.80,0:03:22.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mai...!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.43,0:03:24.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why...?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.01,0:03:27.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mai!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.14,0:03:29.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Why the hell are you still asleep?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.31,0:03:33.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Weren't you supposed to\N wake up if I beat Malik?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.69,0:03:36.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I... knocked that bastard Malik out,\N didn't I?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.82,0:03:37.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.91,0:03:44.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.41,0:03:46.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won, didn't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.12,0:03:47.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Big brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.62,0:03:53.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, you see... you lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.17,0:03:54.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What did you say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.88,0:03:56.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way that's true!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.42,0:03:59.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I Summoned Gearfried,\N and then Malik-
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.17,0:04:01.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you passed out before you could!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.38,0:04:04.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We were so worried about you...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.68,0:04:06.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We thought you were going to die...!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.35,0:04:14.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.94,0:04:17.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Gearfried... The...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.82,0:04:19.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A... ta...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.78,0:04:28.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.49,0:04:31.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So I lost...?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.71,0:04:37.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so sorry, Mai...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.46,0:04:39.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't save you...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.24,0:05:08.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi, you have\N two Monsters on your field...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.95,0:05:12.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since my Blue-Eyes has\N superior Attack Points,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.16,0:05:16.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you must be planning on outlasting me\N by playing Defense Mode for\N the rest of your turns...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.25,0:05:20.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I set two reverse cards!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.71,0:05:22.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Turn end!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.67,0:05:27.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But with my next card, I will\N cut off your only escape route...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.43,0:05:31.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Dammit, Kaiba... \NWhat's he planning next?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.01,0:05:32.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.51,0:05:33.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Draw!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.93,0:05:38.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}No matter what cards\N he's placed face-down,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.94,0:05:43.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}there's still a chance to win so long\N as my Life Points haven't hit zero!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.28,0:05:45.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I have to believe that!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.69,0:05:47.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I set a reverse card!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.74,0:05:51.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, Red-Eyes goes into Defense Mode!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.24,0:05:53.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't run!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.29,0:05:56.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Permanent Trap, activate!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.71,0:05:59.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! A Trap?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.29,0:06:02.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Red-Eyes went back\N into Attack Mode!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.80,0:06:07.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Permanent Trap Card!\N Final Attack Orders!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.09,0:06:10.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As long as this card remains on the field,\N all Monsters remain in Attack Position!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.80,0:06:15.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Furthermore, both players must choose three cards from their decks,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.77,0:06:18.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and place the others in the Graveyard!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.81,0:06:20.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.27,0:06:25.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Now we won't know the winner\N for another three turns.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.36,0:06:33.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The cards I've chosen consist of the required\N formula to create the Ultimate...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.41,0:06:36.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.37,0:06:42.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to clear your head of the\N delusions you have of your\N so-called past in an instant!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.42,0:06:48.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I can only pick three cards from my entire deck...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.13,0:06:51.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But what should I do?\N Which ones should I pick?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.59,0:06:53.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And what about the next match?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.55,0:06:55.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened to Yugi?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.22,0:06:57.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's fighting Kaiba-{\i1}kun{\i0} right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.77,0:06:59.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What!?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.44,0:07:01.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't be {\i1}here{\i0} of all places right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.35,0:07:02.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jounouchi!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.77,0:07:06.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to go watch Yugi's battle!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.53,0:07:07.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Big brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.90,0:07:10.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you! You're still not recovered yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.86,0:07:12.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the patient's condition?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.91,0:07:15.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where's the patient?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.99,0:07:18.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's him...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.16,0:07:19.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wha...?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.37,0:07:22.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He was in critical condition\N just moments ago!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.50,0:07:23.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was moments ago!\N Moments ago!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.83,0:07:25.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And now is now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.09,0:07:27.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's nothin' wrong with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.34,0:07:30.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the great "Perfect Jounouchi" in the flesh,\N makin' a completely miraculous recovery!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.38,0:07:31.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just hold on a moment!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.93,0:07:34.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We still have no idea what even\N happened to you in the first place!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.26,0:07:36.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You still need to be properly tested!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.68,0:07:38.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I said I'm {\i1}fine{\i0}, pal!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.35,0:07:39.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's gun it, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.98,0:07:41.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.48,0:07:46.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The doctor's right...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.36,0:07:48.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have to do what your\N medical overseer tells you to!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.78,0:07:52.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I get what's goin' on in my body\N more than any of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.70,0:07:53.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You {\i1}don't{\i0} know!!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.86,0:07:56.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You were practically {\i1}dead{\i0}\N just minutes ago, you know!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.66,0:07:58.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've all been {\i1}worried sick{\i0} over you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.99,0:08:02.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And here you are, making that face\N like nothing happened...!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.16,0:08:07.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You need to worry about your {\i1}body{\i0}\N before you start thinking about {\i1}Dueling{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.00,0:08:09.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anzu...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.59,0:08:10.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.67,0:08:13.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I have to go do this!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.63,0:08:14.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter what!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.76,0:08:16.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jounouchi!!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.51,0:08:20.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I really am sorry\N for worrying you all.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.93,0:08:25.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But Yugi's not the only one\N concerned about his battles!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.60,0:08:28.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to fight as well in order\N to keep my promise with him!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.52,0:08:31.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your... promise with him...?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.90,0:08:37.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I fight because I\N promised Jounouchi-{\i0}kun{\i1}.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.62,0:08:44.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our Battle City isn't over until\N I settle things with Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.96,0:08:50.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Both Yugi and me have been fighting\N in order to reach the point when we\N can call ourselves True Duelists!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.88,0:08:53.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't matter {\i1}who{\i0}\N it is we're Dueling.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.38,0:08:55.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're connected to each another.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.43,0:08:58.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So I want to watch how it ends!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.47,0:09:01.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to watch Yugi's battle!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.52,0:09:02.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I {\i1}have{\i0} to go!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.98,0:09:04.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jounouchi...!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.02,0:09:08.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shizuka, take care of Mai!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.65,0:09:13.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't push yourself too hard,\N okay big brother?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.36,0:09:15.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait a moment, you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.87,0:09:18.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I apologize!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.99,0:09:21.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oi! Wait up!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.37,0:09:23.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know {\i1}what{\i0}\N to do with them...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.91,0:09:27.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yugi! Don't lose!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.50,0:09:34.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What are Kaiba's\N last three cards...?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.51,0:09:35.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Think...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.76,0:09:37.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Read his strategy...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.63,0:09:41.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}More importantly, I have to decide on the three cards I will choose.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.51,0:09:46.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He hasn't played his Resurrection of the Dead Magic Card in this Duel yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.77,0:09:50.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}In order to reach the highest Attack Power he can possibly reach at this point...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.23,0:09:54.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...he's going to have to use Resurrection of the Dead to bring back the third Blue-Eyes on his field.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.28,0:10:00.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And if he's planning to fuse the three Blue-Eyes into the Ultimate...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.16,0:10:09.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm going to have to gamble\N with this strategy!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.75,0:10:10.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Turn end!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.88,0:10:12.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Finally made a decision, did you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.75,0:10:16.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, regardless of the cards you chose,\N they may as well be deemed useless!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.34,0:10:18.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not possible for you to defeat me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.63,0:10:20.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn! Draw!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.68,0:10:26.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This time you're {\i1}finished{\i0}, Yugi...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.77,0:10:29.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Magic Card!\N Resurrection of the Dead, activate!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.56,0:10:31.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So he did use it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.31,0:10:36.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And the Monster I bring back is,\N of {\i1}course{\i0}, the Blue-Eyes White Dragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.41,0:10:47.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I'll then activate my reverse Magic!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.58,0:10:53.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What?! He already had\N Fusion as a reverse set on the field!?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.09,0:10:56.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Become one being,\N my three Blue-Eyes!!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.06,0:11:10.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Blue-Eyes Ultimate Dragon!!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.81,0:11:15.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Blue-Eyes Ultimate Dragon...!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.48,0:11:20.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The strongest Monster in existence...\N It's Attack Points even surpass Obelisk's!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.32,0:11:21.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Paying attention, Yugi?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.91,0:11:26.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the {\i1}ultimate{\i0} Monster that\N will pave the road of my future!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.63,0:11:45.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi, I'm about to defeat you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.72,0:11:47.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And when I do,\N I'll obtain something {\i1}great{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.60,0:11:53.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it's not something as boringly\N cliched as revenge against you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.61,0:11:58.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why have I fixated\N on fighting you for so long?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.57,0:12:02.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I fought through Battle City in order\N to find the answer to that...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.78,0:12:05.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I finally {\i1}found{\i0} the answer...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.74,0:12:06.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The answer...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.62,0:12:07.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.08,0:12:14.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That stone palette and everything behind it\N rose the curtains on Battle City.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.83,0:12:17.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And {\i1}that{\i0} is where the answer lies.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.88,0:12:23.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi, you've fought in order to regain\N the {\i1}memories{\i0} carved on that palette...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.55,0:12:29.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chasing a past that has\N already gone by is nothing but a\N foolish act and a waste of time!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.60,0:12:30.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The past...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.81,0:12:32.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm not like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.48,0:12:37.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To me, the memory of the past is as\N meaningless to me as a\N crumbling piece of rock!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.53,0:12:44.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When us two siblings lost\N our parents at a young age,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.61,0:12:48.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,those filthy adults forced us\N to live in an orphanage...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.78,0:12:51.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, when we were adopted\N by Gozaburo Kaiba,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.25,0:12:56.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that monster of a family forced us to live\N the worst possible life and undergo an\N elite education with no end in sight.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.75,0:13:00.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And in order to survive in a world filled\N with conspiracy and scheming,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.63,0:13:02.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I underwent any and all\N tests given to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.55,0:13:06.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaiba Corporation was\N destroyed and reborn again.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.22,0:13:09.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But even after I took my revenge,\N I was filled with a {\i1}new{\i0} anger!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.06,0:13:13.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My past is nothing\N but hatred and anger!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.73,0:13:16.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not like your\N stupid fantasy world!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.98,0:13:19.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I only care about the {\i1}future{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.44,0:13:22.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I trample on the past\N as if it never even existed!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.19,0:13:25.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi! You represent the past!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.57,0:13:30.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Once I destroy you, I will shine light down\N the bright corridors of my future!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.49,0:13:34.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At the moment I\N obtain the title of Duel King!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.20,0:13:36.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Kaiba...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.00,0:13:43.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}My brother wants to beat Yugi\N so he can forget about the past?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.80,0:13:49.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Things were hard back then...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.35,0:13:52.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But they weren't {\b0}as{\b1} bad\N when I was with my brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.60,0:13:55.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}No... They were actually {\b0}fun{\b1}\N when I was around big brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.93,0:13:56.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But then...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.44,0:14:06.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Will he even forget the smile\N he showed me so long ago...?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.24,0:14:10.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I will defeat you\N and stand at the top!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.82,0:14:12.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That time has finally come!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.20,0:14:18.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm surprised even {\i1}you{\i0}\N can laugh in this situation...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.62,0:14:23.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaiba, you're one of the few people\N I recognize as a Duelist.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.09,0:14:24.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm a bit disappointed in you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.63,0:14:26.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What{\i0} did you say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.13,0:14:27.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll put it {\i1}bluntly{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.72,0:14:28.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anger...!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.84,0:14:29.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hatred...!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.72,0:14:32.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how much you have,\N those things aren't enough to beat me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.31,0:14:36.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To be frank, I'm {\i1}pitying{\i0} you\N right now for trying to coerce\N me with such trash talk...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.85,0:14:39.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see if you still feel that way\N {\i1}after{\i0} seeing this card...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.23,0:14:42.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Reverse card, open!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.23,0:14:44.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Double Magic, activate!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.07,0:14:45.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.19,0:14:46.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Double Magic?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.57,0:14:47.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Indeed it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.44,0:14:52.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This card lets me use any\N of the Magic Cards the opponent\N used for this turn only!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.16,0:14:54.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Resurrection of the Dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.16,0:14:56.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And Fusion!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.75,0:15:00.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I Summon Buster Blader\N using Resurrection of the Dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.58,0:15:03.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I'll activate Fusion!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.05,0:15:08.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I fuse Black Magician together\n with the Buster Blader!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.43,0:15:13.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's going to polymerize\N the Black Magician and Buster Blader?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.89,0:15:23.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Warrior born of this polymerization\N inherits the Special Ability of Buster Blader!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.27,0:15:28.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Its Attack Power goes up by 500 points\N for every Dragon-Type Monster on the field!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.11,0:15:33.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Both the Ultimate Dragon and\N the Red-Eyes are present on the field!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.95,0:15:35.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Allow me to show you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.28,0:15:38.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Mighty Magic Swordsman - \NBlack Paladin!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.88,0:15:52.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're always the type to entertain\N until the very end, Yugi...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.51,0:15:59.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I presume you know that\N Fusion Monsters can't attack on\N the turn they're Summoned!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.06,0:16:00.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn is over.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.48,0:16:01.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's my turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.85,0:16:02.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Draw!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.19,0:16:05.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Kaiba...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.27,0:16:08.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Your hatred...\N Your anger...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.32,0:16:12.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The card I'm about to set\N will dispose of it all!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.32,0:16:14.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I set a reverse card!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.24,0:16:16.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Turn end!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.33,0:16:17.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.87,0:16:18.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Draw!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.71,0:16:27.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi, I'm about to destroy\N you along with the abominable past!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.21,0:16:28.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'd better prepare yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.59,0:16:29.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaiba!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.96,0:16:32.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those without a past\N {\i1}have{\i0} no future to grasp!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.59,0:16:33.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.93,0:16:36.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The past forms the {\i1}foundation{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.26,0:16:38.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And the future is built on {\i1}top{\i0} of it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.35,0:16:40.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}No one's{\i0} past is meaningless!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.93,0:16:45.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The past, present and future\N are what holds you together!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.44,0:16:47.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmph, I already told you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.44,0:16:50.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That I'm only interested in the {\i1}future{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.19,0:16:51.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Big brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.90,0:16:55.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will surpass Battle City and\N everything that comes after it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.24,0:17:00.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I {\i1}alone{\i0} will be crowned Duel King and\N rise to a higher plane of being!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.41,0:17:05.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaiba, your mind is like this\N Duel Tower standing in the ruins!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.21,0:17:10.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can pile hate on top of hate\N to reach the top, but you'll never\N achieve {\i1}true victory{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.84,0:17:14.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You will wander forever, seeking the\N next hate and the one beyond {\i1}that{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.63,0:17:20.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even {\i1}if{\i0} you manage to\N defeat me, you will only find\N an {\i1}endless chain{\i0} of hatred!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.51,0:17:24.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You will wallow eternally in hatred,\N never able to escape the darkness!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.44,0:17:28.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Heh! Hatred and anger give me {\i1}power{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.98,0:17:31.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The power to {\i1}dominate everything{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.15,0:17:35.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then hit me with all of your \Npent up hatred and anger!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.61,0:17:37.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you think you can\N defeat me with that!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.87,0:17:39.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Humph! Prattle on as you like!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.99,0:17:42.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But victory has already\N chosen {\i1}me{\i0} on this turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.91,0:17:43.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here I come!!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.62,0:17:46.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ultimate Dragon, attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.17,0:17:49.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You won't defeat me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.38,0:17:51.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I always fight for those who believe!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.09,0:17:53.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}For my friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.42,0:17:54.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}For myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.22,0:17:58.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And to become a True Duelist!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.26,0:18:03.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Kaiba, I will defeat you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.06,0:18:07.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}As a rival who walked the\N road of battle with me...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.73,0:18:09.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And as a {\b0}friend{\b1}!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.27,0:18:11.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ultimate Burst!!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.36,0:18:18.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Reverse card, open!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.82,0:18:20.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Magician's Spellbook!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.20,0:18:21.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Futile!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.45,0:18:24.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I activate Magic Absorption!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.41,0:18:29.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The moment your Monster's\N Attack Power goes up,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.67,0:18:34.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,those points are absorbed and\N ejected into my Monster's \NAttack Power, increasing it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.17,0:18:41.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The Ultimate's Attack Power\N went up another 500 points!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.72,0:18:50.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shatter to pieces along with\N Black Paladin and your friend's card,\N Red-Eyes, Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.53,0:18:56.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The end.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.61,0:18:58.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.99,0:19:01.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.08,0:19:05.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi!!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.00,0:19:08.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.71,0:19:10.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that {\i1}so{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.67,0:19:12.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaiba...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.58,0:19:14.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can pile hatred on hatred...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.29,0:19:16.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...but it's {\i1}fragile{\i0}!!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.26,0:19:17.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What was that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.17,0:19:22.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you really think you could win\N bearing things like anger and hatred?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.97,0:19:24.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut your mouth!!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.05,0:19:27.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way your Monster\N could defeat the Ultimate!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.52,0:19:29.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I'm going to show you...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.23,0:19:31.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...the last attack\N that will grant my victory!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.60,0:19:33.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Reverse card, open!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.07,0:19:36.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fusion Cancel!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.23,0:19:38.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Fusion Cancel...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.90,0:19:44.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It splits up one Fusion Monster \Non the field and negates their\N attack for the turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.24,0:19:48.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Did he know I was going to\N play the Ultimate...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.00,0:19:55.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}My Ultimate Dragon...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.59,0:19:57.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...is splitting apart!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.76,0:20:07.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are now two more\N Dragon-Types on the field!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.06,0:20:09.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Increasing Black Paladin's Attack Points!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.39,0:20:16.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And because the fusion of Ultimate was\N canceled, your turn comes to an end!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.90,0:20:18.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.11,0:20:19.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.53,0:20:20.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Draw!!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.61,0:20:25.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaiba! This card will tear apart the\N darkness that controls your heart!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.87,0:20:29.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I activate a Magic Card\N from my hand!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.12,0:20:30.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Diffusion Wave Motion!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.83,0:20:32.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Diffusion Wave Motion!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.96,0:20:35.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By paying 1000 of my Life Points,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.33,0:20:40.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can direct my Magician's attack order\N to cover every Monster on\N your side of the field!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.84,0:20:46.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That means Black Paladin can attack\N all three Blue-Eyes at the {\i1}same time{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.97,0:20:50.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Each of the Blue-Eyes has \N3000 Attack Points...!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.43,0:20:53.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And his Black Paladin has 4900!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.77,0:20:55.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Attack, Black Paladin!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.40,0:21:02.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Kaiba...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.53,0:21:05.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Hatred does not lead to true victory!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.78,0:21:07.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Beyond Magic! Fierce Slashing Wave!!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.86,0:21:39.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Kaiba...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.02,0:21:42.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You {\b0}had{\b1} to lose to me...\N so you can defeat your own madness!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.66,0:21:50.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.49,0:21:51.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yugi won!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.33,0:21:54.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yugi tells a confused Kaiba-{\i0}kun{\i1}...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.33,0:21:58.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's true I won and you lost.\N But we have no difference in skill!"
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.00,0:22:02.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And, "My rival... My friend...\N Why does this line stand between us?!"
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.21,0:22:07.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And an outraged Kaiba-{\i0}kun{\i1} replies,\N "I don't need the strength of friends!"
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.09,0:22:08.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Which causes Jounouchi\N to confront him!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.43,0:22:11.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Eh?! "This time you're gonna Duel {\b0}me{\b1}!"
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.26,0:22:13.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Are you nuts?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.18,0:22:13.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Next time!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.93,0:22:17.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The Deadbeat's Road of Flame:\N Jounouchi VS Kaiba"
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.19,0:22:18.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Duel standby!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.34,0:22:32.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The houses lined down the street drifting by being dyed red
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.68,0:22:40.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If I notice pain, it'll turn into happiness
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.27,0:22:51.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Every time people wipe away tears, they understand bonds
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.37,0:23:01.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The warm strength that you gave me will change into kindness
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.79,0:23:10.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Overflowing feelings don't stop
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.05,0:23:20.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'll live while I feel it, for me to be myself
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.90,0:23:29.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Healed by overflowing friendship
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.16,0:23:35.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Our fated encounter is a truth,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.56,0:23:44.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and someday we'll be able to understand each other
